parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description: The end of the time range to query. By default, the value is the time when the GetResourceConfigurationTimeline operation is called.

parameters.name: Limit
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Valid values: 1 to 100. Default value: 10.

parameters.name: MemberId
parameters.description: This parameter is unavailable since 00:00:00 on June 30, 2021. Account group-related operations are provided as an alternative after 00:00:00 on May 30, 2021. If you are using this parameter, we recommend that you switch to account group-related operations after 00:00:00 on May 30, 2021. For information about account groups, see [Overview](~~211534~~).

parameters.name: MultiAccount
parameters.description: This parameter is unavailable since 00:00:00 on June 30, 2021. Account group-related operations are provided as an alternative after 00:00:00 on May 30, 2021. If you are using this parameter, we recommend that you switch to account group-related operations after 00:00:00 on May 30, 2021. For information about account groups, see [Overview](~~211534~~).

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The pagination token that is used in the next request to retrieve a new page of results. You do not need to specify this parameter for the first request.

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: The beginning of the time range to query. By default, Cloud Config retrieves the configuration changes in the last 30 days for the specified resource.
